Government Refinance Sheet: - For the year 2024-2025, Reference No. 3 There is a grant-in-aid system for zonal and Koda blocks as per the Government Decision dated 15/10/2025. The government's decision. 4 is as follows: -

"For this purpose, the Accountant, CRODA and Youth Services, Pune is being declared as the Drawing and Disbursing Officer and Commissioner, CRODAB Youth Services, Maharashtra State, Pune as the Controlling Officer. "

"For this, the respective Divisional Deputy Director of Sports for the Divisional Koda Complex, the respective District Koda Officer for the District Koda Complex are being declared as the Drawing and Disbursing Officer and Commissioner, HIST B Youth Services, Maharashtra State, Pune as the Controlling Officer. "
Other orders and provisions of the Government Decision shall continue.
2. To make the said Government Corrigendum available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
